<!--
The dimens file contains all dimensions (things related to pixels) that are used
throughout the app. The dimens defined here are general and have no knowledge for what
they are used. They should also not be referenced directly from any layout definition under
res/layout. Instead a style should be defined under res/values/styles.xml that is used in the
layout and references this dimensions.

You should not be in need to define additional dimensions. Instead try to use general dimensions defined here. This
way the UI will be more consistent and look more badass.
-->
